# Fellowship of Essential Oils: Gergely Hollodi Membership Interview

A featured transcript highlight from the **Beyond the Essential Oil Recipe Summit**, hosted by **Elizabeth Ashley**, interviewing **Gergely Hollodi**, co-creator of the *Beyond the Essential Oil Recipe Summit* and publisher of *Aromatica* magazine in Hungary.

